tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE machine_learning_models (
 model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 model_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 model_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
 training_data TEXT,
 model_path VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
 prediction_endpoint VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
 );

CREATE TABLE model_deployments (
    deployment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(255),
    model_description TEXT,
    deployed_date TIMESTAMP,
    deployment_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    deployment_id INT,
    input_data JSONB,
    prediction_result JSONB,
    prediction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name STRING,
    model_type STRING,
    training_date DATE,
    training_accuracy FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT,
    input_data STRING,
    prediction_result STRING,
    prediction_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username STRING,
    email STRING,
    registration_date DATE,
    last_login_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE predictions (
  prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  deployment_id INT REFERENCES deployments(deployment_id),
  input_data JSONB NOT NULL,
  prediction_result JSONB NOT NULL,
  prediction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE ModelDeployments (
    deployment_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT NOT NULL,
    deployment_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    deployment_status VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    deployment_url VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE UserPredictions (
    user_prediction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    prediction_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_feedback VARCHAR(200),
    user_rating INT
);
